  "texts": [
    "1 We included all articles that fulfilled the following inclusion criteria: primary research studies that validate a generative AI for diagnosis.",
    "We applied the following exclusion criteria to our search: review articles, case reports, comments, editorials, and retracted articles.",
    "Titles and abstracts were screened before full-text screening.",
    "Data was extracted using a predefined data extraction sheet.",
    "A count of excluded studies, including the reason for exclusion, was recorded in a PRISMA flow diagram."
  ]
}